funjoin
------------------------------------------
Split separated input into files

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.7-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/sjmulder/funjoin

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/sjmulder/funjoin/archive/refs/tags/1.0.2.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack funjoin-1.0.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./funjoin-1.0.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/funjoin-1.0.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/funjoin-1.0.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(funjoin)
  /usr/bin/funjoin.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/funjoin.README
  /usr/share/doc/funjoin/CHANGELOG.md
  /usr/share/doc/funjoin/LICENSE.md
  /usr/share/doc/funjoin/README.md
  /usr/share/man/man1/funjoin.1.gz

